{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerForPushNotificationsWith:","role":"symbol","title":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary","text":"NSDictionary"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tags","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"tags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set during registration.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Supported value types: NSString, NSNumber, NSArray (for list tags)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Combines push notification registration with tag assignment in a single operation.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This is more efficient than calling registerForPushNotifications and setTags separately,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as tags are sent to the server along with the registration request."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method when you have user attributes available at the time of registration,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as during onboarding or after user authentication.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register with user attributes after sign-up:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class SignUpCoordinator {","","    func completeSignUp(user: User, source: SignUpSource) {","        let registrationTags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_source\": source.analyticsValue,","            \"signup_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","            \"interests\": user.selectedInterests,","            \"language\": Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\",","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(with: registrationTags)","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id)","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(user.email)","    }","}","","extension Bundle {","    var appVersion: String {","        infoDictionary?[\"CFBundleShortVersionString\"] as? String ?? \"unknown\"","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Registers the device for push notifications with initial tags.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswith:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerForPushNotificationsWith:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/registerForPushNotificationsWith:":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswith:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerForPushNotificationsWith:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers the device for push notifications with initial tags."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]}}}